        boolean execute(org.bukkit.command.CommandSender sender,
              java.lang.String label,
              java.lang.String[] args)
        This will be callen if the command has be executed.
        Parameters:
        sender - The CommandSender that has executed the command.
        label - The label of the executed command (will be the alias or something like that).
        args - The arguments of the executed command (will be a String[]).
        Returns:
        Has to return true if command has been handled, otherwise false.
